### 7. STUDENT ROUTES (/api/student)
### ============================================================
# Replace BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT below with the token from 5.2.

### 7.1 Get my classes (Student)

GET http://localhost:5001/api/student/me/classes
Authorization: Bearer BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT



### 7.2 Get my attendance (optionally filtered by class)

# Without filter (all classes)

GET http://localhost:5001/api/student/me/attendance
Authorization: Bearer BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT

###
# With specific class filter

GET http://localhost:5001/api/student/me/attendance?class_id=CLASS_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT



### 7.3 Get my grades (optionally filtered by term)

# All grades

GET http://localhost:5001/api/student/me/grades
Authorization: Bearer BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT

###
# Grades for specific term (e.g. 2025-S1)

GET http://localhost:5001/api/student/me/grades?term=2025-S1
Authorization: Bearer BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT



### 7.4 Get my schedule

GET http://localhost:5001/api/student/me/schedule
Authorization: Bearer BEARER_TOKEN_STUDENT